name: The Underworld Manipulator
description:
I'm still worried about the animal world being messed with by humans. Have animals been treated according to animal behavior? do they deserve to be tormented by dwelling in their master's house and not being allowed to follow their instincts in the wild world?

Do they deserve to be in the underworld and not appear in the real world
